  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ISLANDS MIGHT FLY</strong> is a tycoon game about managing rotating space station. Recreate historical periods for the richest people of the future. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799400/extras/66033ad8b3b84159a9fed6c62e12b10d.poster.avif?t=1744929097\" width=600 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799400/extras/66033ad8b3b84159a9fed6c62e12b10d.webm?t=1744929097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799400/extras/66033ad8b3b84159a9fed6c62e12b10d.mp4?t=1744929097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the future the richest people of the world will pay to experience different eras: from Ancient Rome to Sengoku period of Japan. You are assigned to create these scenarios in a giant rotating space habitat. Hire engineers and artists to recreate those periods.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799400/extras/f3d6d583af88faf7198137e620d069e1.poster.avif?t=1744929097\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799400/extras/f3d6d583af88faf7198137e620d069e1.webm?t=1744929097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799400/extras/f3d6d583af88faf7198137e620d069e1.mp4?t=1744929097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage engineers and creatives</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create projects and fulfill different scenarios</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build and improve infrastructure</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique mechanics of managing logistics inside rotating space station</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ISLANDS MIGHT FLY</strong> is a tycoon game about managing rotating space station. Recreate historical periods for the richest people of the future. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799400/extras/66033ad8b3b84159a9fed6c62e12b10d.poster.avif?t=1744929097\" width=600 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799400/extras/66033ad8b3b84159a9fed6c62e12b10d.webm?t=1744929097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799400/extras/66033ad8b3b84159a9fed6c62e12b10d.mp4?t=1744929097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the future the richest people of the world will pay to experience different eras: from Ancient Rome to Sengoku period of Japan. You are assigned to create these scenarios in a giant rotating space habitat. Hire engineers and artists to recreate those periods.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799400/extras/f3d6d583af88faf7198137e620d069e1.poster.avif?t=1744929097\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799400/extras/f3d6d583af88faf7198137e620d069e1.webm?t=1744929097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799400/extras/f3d6d583af88faf7198137e620d069e1.mp4?t=1744929097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage engineers and creatives</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create projects